{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create an image card grid of four across (4-column layout) optimized for model photography.
    Each card should display:
    
    Image at the top (full-width, responsive, model-scale ratio — e.g., 3:4 or 4:5).
    
    Product details below the image: product name, price, and a “Shop the Look” button.
    
    The “Shop the Look” button should open a quick-add or modal view allowing users to add multiple products from the look directly to cart (e.g., jacket, shirt, pants, shoes).
    
    Design specs:
    
    Maintain equal spacing and consistent padding between cards.
    
    Cards should stack to two across on tablet and one across on mobile.
    
    Clean typography with minimal overlays — the focus is on the model imagery.
    
    Include hover states for desktop (e.g., light image zoom or button reveal).
    
    Goal:
    
    A visually cohesive, shoppable grid that blends editorial presentation with e-commerce functionality — enabling the customer to experience the look and purchase it seamlessly., I would also like the ability to change the button to a link , Extend the existing Shop the Look Grid section so each Look Card supports:
    
    A linkable “Shop the Look” button (navigates to a collection, campaign, or editorial page).
    
    A bag icon that always opens the quick-add modal.
    
    Full accessibility and responsive behavior consistent with the section.
    
    Requirements (Per Look Card / Block)
    
    Inputs
    
    Image upload (model image)
    
    Recommended aspect ratio 4:5 (accept 3:4 as well)
    
    Up to 8 products assigned (e.g., jacket, knit, pant, shoe, accessory)
    
    Optional Controls
    
    Button Link URL – if present, the “Shop the Look” button navigates to this URL
    
    Bag Icon (👜) – appears to the right of the button text and always opens the quick-add modal
    
    Toggles (per block):
    
    enable_look (show/hide this Look Card)
    
    enable_shop_link (turn the button link on/off)
    
    enable_bag_icon (show/hide the bag icon)
    
    Front-End Behavior
    
    Shop the Look Button (Dual Functionality)
    
    If Link URL provided and enable_shop_link = true → clicking button navigates to that URL
    
    If no Link URL or enable_shop_link = false → button opens modal (default)
    
    Bag Icon
    
    Small, right-aligned bag/shopping cart icon next to button label
    
    Clicking icon (👜) always opens the modal, even if the button itself navigates elsewhere
    
    Modal shows assigned products with:
    
    Variant selectors
    
    Quantity fields
    
    “Include” toggles
    
    Add selected to cart (AJAX bundle add)
    
    User paths
    
    ➜ Click button text → Learn more / visit look page
    
    ➜ Click bag icon → Add items directly from the modal, The bag icon should be on the right side of the image, not next to the SHOP THE LOOK button. Also, I do not have the ability to disable the SHOP THE LOOK button nor change it to a link instead of a button. , The bag icon should be on the bottom right please and I need the ability to make the background of the bag image transparent so that it is not white on top of an image. , When hovering/clicking on the bag icon, the background should be transparent as well. , I would also like the ability to change the order of the looks to make it easier to re-order, I would also like to have the ability to upload an image or video for Shop the Look
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-model-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .ai-model-grid__container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: {{ block.settings.card_spacing }}px;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .ai-model-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.card_background }};
  }

  .ai-model-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}.hidden {
    display: none;
  }

  .ai-model-card__media-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: {{ block.settings.image_aspect_ratio }};
    overflow: hidden;
    background-color: #f4f4f4;
  }

  .ai-model-card__image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94);
  }

  .ai-model-card__video-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  {% if block.settings.enable_image_zoom %}
    .ai-model-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover .ai-model-card__image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }
  {% endif %}

  .ai-model-card__media-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background-color: #f4f4f4;
  }

  .ai-model-card__media-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 60%;
    height: 60%;
    opacity: 0.3;
  }

  .ai-model-card__bag-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 16px;
    right: 16px;
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.bag_icon_background }};
    color: {{ block.settings.bag_icon_color }};
    border: {{ block.settings.button_border_width }}px solid {{ block.settings.bag_icon_border_color }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.button_border_radius }}px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    z-index: 2;
    {% if block.settings.bag_icon_transparent %}
      background-color: transparent;
      border-color: transparent;
    {% endif %}
  }

  .ai-model-card__bag-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    color: {{ block.settings.bag_icon_hover_color }};
    {% if block.settings.bag_icon_transparent %}
      background-color: transparent;
      border-color: transparent;
    {% else %}
      background-color: {{ block.settings.bag_icon_hover_background }};
      border-color: {{ block.settings.bag_icon_hover_border_color }};
    {% endif %}
  }

  .ai-model-card__bag-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
  }

  .ai-model-card__content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding: {{ block.settings.content_padding }}px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-grow: 1;
  }

  .ai-model-card__title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: {{ block.settings.title_font.family }}, {{ block.settings.title_font.fallback_families }};
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.title_font.weight }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.title_size }}px;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    margin: 0;
    text-transform: {{ block.settings.title_transform }};
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .ai-model-card__price-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: {{ block.settings.price_font.family }}, {{ block.settings.price_font.fallback_families }};
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.price_font.weight }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.price_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ai-model-card__actions-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  .ai-model-card__button-{{ ai_gen_id }},
  .ai-model-card__link-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    padding: {{ block.settings.button_padding_vertical }}px {{ block.settings.button_padding_horizontal }}px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.button_background }};
    color: {{ block.settings.button_text_color }};
    border: {{ block.settings.button_border_width }}px solid {{ block.settings.button_border_color }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.button_border_radius }}px;
    font-family: {{ block.settings.button_font.family }}, {{ block.settings.button_font.fallback_families }};
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.button_font.weight }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.button_size }}px;
    text-transform: {{ block.settings.button_transform }};
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    text-align: center;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: block;
  }

  .ai-model-card__button-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover,
  .ai-model-card__link-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.button_hover_background }};
    color: {{ block.settings.button_hover_text_color }};
    border-color: {{ block.settings.button_hover_border_color }};
  }

  .ai-model-modal-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: none;
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
    z-index: 9999;
    overflow-y: auto;
    padding: 20px;
  }

  .ai-model-modal-{{ ai_gen_id }}.active {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .ai-model-modal__content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.modal_background }};
    max-width: 900px;
    width: 100%;
    max-height: 90vh;
    overflow-y: auto;
    position: relative;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.modal_border_radius }}px;
    padding: 40px;
  }

  .ai-model-modal__close-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 20px;
    right: 20px;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 8px;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .ai-model-modal__close-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
  }

  .ai-model-modal__header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }

  .ai-model-modal__title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: {{ block.settings.title_font.family }}, {{ block.settings.title_font.fallback_families }};
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.title_font.weight }};
    font-size: 24px;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    margin: 0 0 8px 0;
    text-transform: {{ block.settings.title_transform }};
  }

  .ai-model-modal__subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .ai-model-modal__products-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }

  .ai-model-modal__product-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 100px 1fr auto;
    gap: 20px;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 20px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-model-modal__product-{{ ai_gen_id }}.disabled {
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .ai-model-modal__product-checkbox-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    cursor: pointer;
    accent-color: {{ block.settings.button_background }};
  }

  .ai-model-modal__product-image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100px;
    height: 100px;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .ai-model-modal__product-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100px;
    height: 100px;
    background-color: #f4f4f4;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .ai-model-modal__product-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    opacity: 0.3;
  }

  .ai-model-modal__product-info-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .ai-model-modal__product-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-family: {{ block.settings.title_font.family }}, {{ block.settings.title_font.fallback_families }};
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.title_font.weight }};
    font-size: 16px;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ai-model-modal__product-price-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
  }

  .ai-model-modal__product-controls-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
    min-width: 200px;
  }

  .ai-model-modal__product-select-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding: 8px 12px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 14px;
    background-color: #ffffff;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .ai-model-modal__product-quantity-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .ai-model-modal__quantity-label-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .ai-model-modal__quantity-input-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 60px;
    padding: 6px 8px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 14px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .ai-model-modal__footer-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .ai-model-modal__total-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 16px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    font-family: {{ block.settings.title_font.family }}, {{ block.settings.title_font.fallback_families }};
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.title_font.weight }};
    font-size: 18px;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
  }

  .ai-model-modal__add-button-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding: 16px 32px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.button_background }};
    color: {{ block.settings.button_text_color }};
    border: {{ block.settings.button_border_width }}px solid {{ block.settings.button_border_color }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.button_border_radius }}px;
    font-family: {{ block.settings.button_font.family }}, {{ block.settings.button_font.fallback_families }};
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.button_font.weight }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.button_size }}px;
    text-transform: {{ block.settings.button_transform }};
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .ai-model-modal__add-button-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.button_hover_background }};
    color: {{ block.settings.button_hover_text_color }};
    border-color: {{ block.settings.button_hover_border_color }};
  }

  .ai-model-modal__add-button-{{ ai_gen_id }}:disabled {
    opacity: 0.5;
    cursor: not-allowed;
  }

  .ai-model-modal__empty-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px 20px;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 989px) {
    .ai-model-grid__container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: {{ block.settings.card_spacing | times: 0.75 }}px;
    }

    .ai-model-card__title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.title_size | times: 0.9 }}px;
    }

    .ai-model-card__price-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.price_size | times: 0.9 }}px;
    }

    .ai-model-modal__content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: 30px 20px;
    }

    .ai-model-modal__product-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: auto 80px 1fr;
      gap: 15px;
    }

    .ai-model-modal__product-image-{{ ai_gen_id }},
    .ai-model-modal__product-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
    }

    .ai-model-modal__product-controls-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
      min-width: auto;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-model-grid__container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: {{ block.settings.card_spacing | times: 0.5 }}px;
    }

    .ai-model-card__content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.content_padding | times: 0.75 }}px;
    }

    .ai-model-card__bag-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<model-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} class="ai-model-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-model-grid__container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    {% liquid
      assign look_order = block.settings.look_order | split: ','
      if look_order.size == 0
        assign look_order = '1,2,3,4' | split: ','
      endif
    %}

    {% for look_num_str in look_order %}
      {% assign i = look_num_str | strip | plus: 0 %}
      {% liquid
        assign look_enabled_key = 'look_' | append: i | append: '_enabled'
        assign look_media_type_key = 'look_' | append: i | append: '_media_type'
        assign look_image_key = 'look_' | append: i | append: '_image'
        assign look_video_key = 'look_' | append: i | append: '_video'
        assign look_title_key = 'look_' | append: i | append: '_title'
        assign look_price_key = 'look_' | append: i | append: '_price'
        assign look_button_text_key = 'look_' | append: i | append: '_button_text'
        assign look_button_link_key = 'look_' | append: i | append: '_button_link'
        assign look_button_type_key = 'look_' | append: i | append: '_button_type'
        assign look_enable_bag_icon_key = 'look_' | append: i | append: '_enable_bag_icon'

        assign look_enabled = block.settings[look_enabled_key]
        assign look_media_type = block.settings[look_media_type_key]
        assign look_image = block.settings[look_image_key]
        assign look_video = block.settings[look_video_key]
        assign look_title = block.settings[look_title_key]
        assign look_price = block.settings[look_price_key]
        assign look_button_text = block.settings[look_button_text_key]
        assign look_button_link = block.settings[look_button_link_key]
        assign look_button_type = block.settings[look_button_type_key]
        assign look_enable_bag_icon = block.settings[look_enable_bag_icon_key]
      %}

      <div class="ai-model-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {% unless look_enabled %}hidden{% endunless %}" data-look-index="{{ i }}">
        <div class="ai-model-card__media-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {% if look_media_type == 'video' and look_video %}
            {{
              look_video
              | video_tag:
                class: 'ai-model-card__video-' | append: ai_gen_id,
                autoplay: true,
                loop: true,
                muted: true,
                controls: false
            }}
          {% elsif look_media_type == 'image' and look_image %}
            <img
              src="{{ look_image | image_url: width: 800 }}"
              alt="{{ look_image.alt | escape }}"
              loading="lazy"
              width="{{ look_image.width }}"
              height="{{ look_image.height }}"
              class="ai-model-card__image-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            >
          {% else %}
            <div class="ai-model-card__media-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {{ 'image' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
            </div>
          {% endif %}

          {% if look_enable_bag_icon %}
            <button
              class="ai-model-card__bag-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              data-bag-trigger="{{ i }}"
              aria-label="Add look {{ i }} to cart"
            >
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M6 2L3 6v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h14a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V6l-3-4z"></path>
                <line x1="3" y1="6" x2="21" y2="6"></line>
                <path d="M16 10a4 4 0 0 1-8 0"></path>
              </svg>
            </button>
          {% endif %}
        </div>

        <div class="ai-model-card__content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {% if look_title != blank %}
            <h3 class="ai-model-card__title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ look_title }}</h3>
          {% endif %}

          {% if look_price != blank %}
            <p class="ai-model-card__price-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ look_price }}</p>
          {% endif %}

          <div class="ai-model-card__actions-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {% if look_button_type == 'link' and look_button_link != blank %}
              <a
                href="{{ look_button_link }}"
                class="ai-model-card__link-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              >
                {% if look_button_text != blank %}
                  {{ look_button_text }}
                {% else %}
                  {{ block.settings.default_button_text }}
                {% endif %}
              </a>
            {% elsif look_button_type == 'modal' %}
              <button
                class="ai-model-card__button-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                data-modal-trigger="{{ i }}"
                aria-label="Shop the look {{ i }}"
              >
                {% if look_button_text != blank %}
                  {{ look_button_text }}
                {% else %}
                  {{ block.settings.default_button_text }}
                {% endif %}
              </button>
            {% elsif look_button_type == 'disabled' %}
            {% endif %}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="ai-model-modal-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-modal="{{ i }}" role="dialog" aria-modal="true">
        <div class="ai-model-modal__content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          <button class="ai-model-modal__close-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-modal-close="{{ i }}" aria-label="Close modal">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"></line>
              <line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"></line>
            </svg>
          </button>

          <div class="ai-model-modal__header-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {% if look_title != blank %}
              <h2 class="ai-model-modal__title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ look_title }}</h2>
            {% endif %}
            <p class="ai-model-modal__subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.modal_subtitle }}</p>
          </div>

          {% assign has_products = false %}
          {% for j in (1..8) %}
            {% liquid
              assign product_key = 'look_' | append: i | append: '_product_' | append: j
              assign product = block.settings[product_key]
              if product != blank
                assign has_products = true
              endif
            %}
          {% endfor %}

          {% if has_products %}
            <div class="ai-model-modal__products-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {% for j in (1..8) %}
                {% liquid
                  assign product_key = 'look_' | append: i | append: '_product_' | append: j
                  assign product = block.settings[product_key]
                %}

                {% if product != blank %}
                  <div class="ai-model-modal__product-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-product-id="{{ product.id }}">
                    <input
                      type="checkbox"
                      class="ai-model-modal__product-checkbox-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                      data-product-checkbox
                      checked
                      aria-label="Include {{ product.title }}"
                    >

                    {% if product.featured_image %}
                      <img
                        src="{{ product.featured_image | image_url: width: 200 }}"
                        alt="{{ product.featured_image.alt | escape }}"
                        class="ai-model-modal__product-image-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                        loading="lazy"
                      >
                    {% else %}
                      <div class="ai-model-modal__product-image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                        {{ 'product-1' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
                      </div>
                    {% endif %}

                    <div class="ai-model-modal__product-info-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                      <h4 class="ai-model-modal__product-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ product.title }}</h4>
                      <p class="ai-model-modal__product-price-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-product-price="{{ product.price }}">
                        {{ product.price | money }}
                      </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="ai-model-modal__product-controls-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                      {% if product.variants.size > 1 %}
                        <select class="ai-model-modal__product-select-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-variant-select>
                          {% for variant in product.variants %}
                            <option
                              value="{{ variant.id }}"
                              data-price="{{ variant.price }}"
                              {% unless variant.available %}disabled{% endunless %}
                            >
                              {{ variant.title }} - {{ variant.price | money }}
                              {% unless variant.available %} (Sold out){% endunless %}
                            </option>
                          {% endfor %}
                        </select>
                      {% else %}
                        <input
                          type="hidden"
                          data-variant-select
                          value="{{ product.first_available_variant.id }}"
                          data-price="{{ product.first_available_variant.price }}"
                        >
                      {% endif %}

                      <div class="ai-model-modal__product-quantity-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                        <span class="ai-model-modal__quantity-label-{{ ai_gen_id }}">Qty:</span>
                        <input
                          type="number"
                          class="ai-model-modal__quantity-input-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                          data-quantity-input
                          value="1"
                          min="1"
                          max="10"
                          aria-label="Quantity for {{ product.title }}"
                        >
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                {% endif %}
              {% endfor %}
            </div>

            <div class="ai-model-modal__footer-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <div class="ai-model-modal__total-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <span>Total:</span>
                <span data-total-price>$0.00</span>
              </div>

              <button class="ai-model-modal__add-button-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-add-to-cart="{{ i }}">
                {{ block.settings.add_to_cart_text }}
              </button>
            </div>
          {% else %}
            <div class="ai-model-modal__empty-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <p>No products added to this look yet. Configure products in the theme editor.</p>
            </div>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</model-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}>

<script>
  (function() {
    class ModelGrid{{ ai_gen_id }} extends HTMLElement {
      constructor() {
        super();
        this.modals = this.querySelectorAll('.ai-model-modal-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
        this.modalTriggers = this.querySelectorAll('[data-modal-trigger]');
        this.bagTriggers = this.querySelectorAll('[data-bag-trigger]');
        this.closeButtons = this.querySelectorAll('[data-modal-close]');
        this.addToCartButtons = this.querySelectorAll('[data-add-to-cart]');
      }

      connectedCallback() {
        this.setupEventListeners();
        this.modals.forEach((modal) => {
          this.updateModalTotal(modal);
        });
      }

      setupEventListeners() {
        this.modalTriggers.forEach((trigger) => {
          trigger.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
            const modalId = e.currentTarget.getAttribute('data-modal-trigger');
            this.openModal(modalId);
          });
        });

        this.bagTriggers.forEach((trigger) => {
          trigger.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
            const modalId = e.currentTarget.getAttribute('data-bag-trigger');
            this.openModal(modalId);
          });
        });

        this.closeButtons.forEach((button) => {
          button.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
            const modalId = e.currentTarget.getAttribute('data-modal-close');
            this.closeModal(modalId);
          });
        });

        this.modals.forEach((modal) => {
          modal.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
            if (e.target === modal) {
              const modalId = modal.getAttribute('data-modal');
              this.closeModal(modalId);
            }
          });

          const checkboxes = modal.querySelectorAll('[data-product-checkbox]');
          checkboxes.forEach((checkbox) => {
            checkbox.addEventListener('change', () => {
              const productRow = checkbox.closest('.ai-model-modal__product-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
              if (checkbox.checked) {
                productRow.classList.remove('disabled');
              } else {
                productRow.classList.add('disabled');
              }
              this.updateModalTotal(modal);
            });
          });

          const variantSelects = modal.querySelectorAll('[data-variant-select]');
          variantSelects.forEach((select) => {
            select.addEventListener('change', () => {
              this.updateProductPrice(select);
              this.updateModalTotal(modal);
            });
          });

          const quantityInputs = modal.querySelectorAll('[data-quantity-input]');
          quantityInputs.forEach((input) => {
            input.addEventListener('change', () => {
              this.updateModalTotal(modal);
            });
          });
        });

        this.addToCartButtons.forEach((button) => {
          button.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
            const modalId = e.currentTarget.getAttribute('data-add-to-cart');
            this.addToCart(modalId, button);
          });
        });

        document.addEventListener('keydown', (e) => {
          if (e.key === 'Escape') {
            this.modals.forEach((modal) => {
              if (modal.classList.contains('active')) {
                const modalId = modal.getAttribute('data-modal');
                this.closeModal(modalId);
              }
            });
          }
        });
      }

      updateProductPrice(select) {
        const productRow = select.closest('.ai-model-modal__product-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
        const priceDisplay = productRow.querySelector('[data-product-price]');
        const selectedOption = select.options ? select.options[select.selectedIndex] : select;
        const price = selectedOption.getAttribute('data-price');
        
        if (priceDisplay && price) {
          priceDisplay.textContent = this.formatMoney(price);
          priceDisplay.setAttribute('data-product-price', price);
        }
      }

      updateModalTotal(modal) {
        const products = modal.querySelectorAll('.ai-model-modal__product-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
        let total = 0;

        products.forEach((product) => {
          const checkbox = product.querySelector('[data-product-checkbox]');
          if (checkbox && checkbox.checked) {
            const variantSelect = product.querySelector('[data-variant-select]');
            const quantityInput = product.querySelector('[data-quantity-input]');
            const selectedOption = variantSelect.options ? variantSelect.options[variantSelect.selectedIndex] : variantSelect;
            const price = parseInt(selectedOption.getAttribute('data-price'));
            const quantity = parseInt(quantityInput.value) || 1;
            
            total += price * quantity;
          }
        });

        const totalDisplay = modal.querySelector('[data-total-price]');
        if (totalDisplay) {
          totalDisplay.textContent = this.formatMoney(total);
        }
      }

      formatMoney(cents) {
        const amount = (cents / 100).toFixed(2);
        return `$${amount}`;
      }

      openModal(modalId) {
        const modal = this.querySelector(`[data-modal="${modalId}"]`);
        if (modal) {
          modal.classList.add('active');
          document.body.style.overflow = 'hidden';
        }
      }

      closeModal(modalId) {
        const modal = this.querySelector(`[data-modal="${modalId}"]`);
        if (modal) {
          modal.classList.remove('active');
          document.body.style.overflow = '';
        }
      }

      async addToCart(modalId, button) {
        const modal = this.querySelector(`[data-modal="${modalId}"]`);
        const products = modal.querySelectorAll('.ai-model-modal__product-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
        const items = [];

        products.forEach((product) => {
          const checkbox = product.querySelector('[data-product-checkbox]');
          if (checkbox && checkbox.checked) {
            const variantSelect = product.querySelector('[data-variant-select]');
            const quantityInput = product.querySelector('[data-quantity-input]');
            const quantity = parseInt(quantityInput.value) || 1;
            
            if (variantSelect && variantSelect.value) {
              items.push({
                id: variantSelect.value,
                quantity: quantity
              });
            }
          }
        });

        if (items.length === 0) {
          return;
        }

        button.disabled = true;
        button.textContent = 'Adding...';

        try {
          const response = await fetch('/cart/add.js', {
            method: 'POST',
            headers: {
              'Content-Type': 'application/json',
            },
            body: JSON.stringify({ items })
          });

          if (response.ok) {
            button.textContent = 'Added!';
            setTimeout(() => {
              button.textContent = '{{ block.settings.add_to_cart_text }}';
              button.disabled = false;
              this.closeModal(modalId);
              
              if (window.theme && window.theme.cart) {
                window.theme.cart.refresh();
              }
              
              document.documentElement.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('cart:refresh', {
                bubbles: true
              }));
            }, 1000);
          } else {
            throw new Error('Failed to add to cart');
          }
        } catch (error) {
          button.textContent = 'Error - An item is out of stock';
          button.disabled = false;
          console.error('Error adding to cart:', error);
        }
      }
    }

    customElements.define('model-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}', ModelGrid{{ ai_gen_id }});
  })();
</script>

